headline: 2 Reasons to Like MOH and 1 to Stay Skeptical
summary: Molina Healthcare’s stock price has taken a beating over the past six months, shedding 44.8% of its value and falling to $179.15 per share. This was partly due to its softer quarterly results and may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
